name: Samuel Hübinette
bio: Father of 3 and married to @stinastunts . Two time Formula Drift Champion. Rally Cross X-Games 🎖 . Movie and Commercial Stunt Driver.

social_posts.post_text:
A throwback to myself racing in the Traxxas Torc Off Road Series . Claimed 7 podiums out of 14 races in my rookie season.
Having @21robmac as a teammate was such a blast. You can watch a video on the link in my profile . #traxxasracing #mopar #bfgoodrich #waybackwednesday

A wayback to the summer of 2008 I believe . Competing in the Camaro Cup of Sweden for Bryntesson Motorsports . And multi touring car racing champion @thedbjork had us over for dinner and came out to support .
When in Aspen 😎

What a fun one this was. Here is the second snow shoot I’ve done with the TRX . After last year getting to drive it I was sold . When I got back home I ordered one and got a say it’s the best vehicle I’ve ever had. We shot this last week and to watch it finished a week later tells you how talented the @racingcowboys Crew is. Happy holidays to ya all and keep it sideways 💪🏻 #hübinettestunts

Got some upgrades sent to us from @crazycartofficial . Getting them ready for the annual Christmas light cruise in our neighborhood. This is a great tool for yourself or the kids to get used to sideways drift driving .
Christmas came early for us. Let me introduce Willow. Yep 👍
Thank you Traxxas for the best RC products out there . @traxxas #myfirstbackflip

Happy anniversary to us on this day. I would not be where I’m at without your amazing love and support. What a multi talented woman you are and I could not dream of a better mother to our children. 16 years went by definitely way too fast ,so let’s enjoy each day like it’s our last Hunny Bunny . Let’s GO !!! Love you 🙏
2023 let’s GO!!!! Happy new year you all. A new year with new opportunities for something greater in life. Live your best life NOW. It’s going way too fast . #newyears #blessedlife #family

Shocking news about Ken. He took the driving to another level with his creative ideas and marketing skills . It was a blast getting to race him in Rally Cross. Prayers for his family during this incredible hard time . #sad
KEN BLOCK the legend 👊Video courtesy @derosetim . #legendsneverdie
It’s Friday so let’s get this weekend GOING. #noelectricbill #waybackfriday
Adorable duo from inside to outside right here. #loves
Stina out staying in shape for the next car commercial or movie 🎥. @stinastunts #hübinettestunts
Very impressive snow mass they got in the sierra mountains. Over all 12 meter snow this season as of now 😂 #californiaadventure
What a treat getting to explore Malibu mountains from the sky .And great conversations over lunch in Oxnard .  Appreciate it Ken. @kenarlidge
Now I just need to figure out how to get it rear wheel drive too, like the new Raptor. Stoked about this truck just wish I could choose rear wheel drive setting. Help me @ramtrucks 😎

With the #bushlightclash coming up this weekend at the coliseum in LA I wanted to tell you all, myslef and Earnhart (Rhys) are ready for battle . I want to say thank you to Kellogg's for believing in the FIRST ever Swede to race for this event 💪🏻😎💪🏻 #itsajokepeople
Happy valentine to my favorite dance partner ever. Enjoying every moment in life with you my love. @stinastunts
Fun getting to work with your wife , here ON set for Dodge . #hübinettestunts @stinastunts
Such a great spot to be part of .Great times with @rhysmillenracing @tannerfoust @mossnow DP @macgregor.works and our extra ordinary Director @therealmarky  Just to mention a few. #nascar75
Some BTS of a shoot I was a stunt Cordinator for .
Boat season is back . Let’s go !!
Rad low flying DC3 💪🏻 #carcommercial
Back to one 👊 Ford vs Ferrari movie 🎥. #tbt

This is from the first test day for the upcoming movie FERRARI directed by Michael Mann. This was my first day in the car and the team from England built some great movie cars for us with the help from @rpnagle our stunt Cordinator. You get so much respect for the race car drivers from the 50s being so exposed in these F1 cars . #mikehawthorn #stuntdouble #ferrari #actor #hübinettestunts

There is a massive need of safe clean water in our world. Myself and Stina have been supporting Oneattatime for many years and they are making a difference, specially with all your help. If you go to verabradley.com and purchase a water bottle they will donate to Oneattatime. Direct link in my profile . Let’s help all these kids that can’t get safe water . #safewater #helpkids #cleanwaterforall @verabradley @oneattatime
The Wall. #advertising #tbt
Sunday drive👌  #hübinettestunts
Always a pleasure to tear up someone else brand new car. #hübinettestunts
Love this crew . #familyfirst @mammothmountain #700inchesofsnow

What an amazing weekend to get inducted as one of the first to Hall of Fame of Drifting. Very grateful to Formula Drift with @ryanjsage and @jimliaw for what they have done over the years. Getting to share this with my old rival and great friend @rhysmillenracing was such a blast.
Thank you @formulad and all of you fans and supporters who came out. #halloffame #formuladrift #formulad

The movie Ferrari coming down to its final tweaks . Got to play a part as Mike Hawthorn, the first British F1 champion for Enzo’s team .It was something I’ve never done before and definitely out of my comfort. But that’s how you grow and Man do I respect actors for what they do. I got to watch some of it today in the studio and it looks awesome. Thank you Robert Nagle for the opportunity. #ferrari #bts
Miss my good old Lambo. Maybe it’s time to get a new toy. What would you suggest for a Supercar ?

A behind the scenes film from a project we did with Lamborghini Newport Beach. A no budget film we put together with lots of friends help. Just to mention a few. Directed by @antony_hoffman_  Lambo Driver @stinastunts Ducati bike rider @flying_franco with @purki1 holding on for her life. Stunt coordinator @huntergostunts and I got to co produce it. Watch the actual Film at the link in my profile #hübinettestunts

One of the fun perks being in this industry is you get to have many different looks and in this case @davebautista for me. Powers and myself on set working as Stunt Doubles for the movie Stars . @elebardha Stunt Coordinating and always a blast working with you brother. Thank you for having us 💪🏻 #movie #stuntwork #waybackmonday
Enjoy this awesome RAM TRX special edition commercial that myself and Rich Rutherford got to be part of . Directed by @schneider_photo with his @porchhouse.co team.

Happy Mother’s Day to all the awesome Moms out there. And a special shout out to this amazing Mom on this day. Thank you for ALL you do for us all. Come home from your stunt job so we can celebrate you babe 💪🏻 We love you ❤️ #mothersday
Some behind the scenes shots from the making of the TRX Lunar edition shoot a few weeks back with  @porchhouse.co #hübinettestunts
Such a beautiful sleeper . Looking forward to see what we can do with this master piece . With the options to get in to 2WD there should be some possibilities for rear wheel spins and over steer 😎
Loving life with my amazing wife and best friend . Today Sweden against Denmark in @iihfhockey World Cup of Hockey. Kom igen nu grabbar, nu tar vi Danskarna och sedan USA imorgon. #sverigerockarfett
While vacationing here in AZ me and Stina went by @az__demon to see his car collection. Lots of @dodgeofficial HP in that garage. Thanks for the tour Robb . Next Time let’s DRIVE them 😎
It’s been a rough week 😎How is your week looking like ?

That’s a wrap with @porchhouse.co production house and @publicissapient . This is a BTS clip so stay tuned for the actual commercials we created .This is the Hellcat Redeye with 808 HP 💪🏻#hübinettestunts
Happy birthday Foxy Foust . @tannerfoust
Someone you want to have on your side . His name is Officer KING.  #hübinettestunts
Wake maker fun 💪🏻#summerfun
A fun throwback when I took my son out for his first drift ride .Professional driver on closed course! #myson #myminime #hübinettestunts #tbt

Thanks to @samuel_hubinette for joining me on the first episode of the Automotive Filmmakers Podcast. Check out the full episode on my YouTube channel. 

#stuntdriver #filmmaking #podcast #samuelhubinette
Enjoying our summer tour of Sweden 🇸🇪 visiting friends and family .
Heading out for dinner in a Water Taxi is definitely rad. And what a beautiful coastline they got here in Italy 🇮🇹.

The first event when NASCAR and Drifting met. It was such a blast watching the NASCAR guys trying to drift our cars and see how they were struggling going sideways in a right hand corner . Left turns went pretty good due to some of them coming from dirt circle racing like @tonystuart_ for example. #tbt

This was a fun one with Rich Rutherford in Texas. Produced by @porchhouse.co with Director Andrew Schneider. Hoping Dodge will continue doing this type of marketing for a long time 💪🏻 Agency @publicissapient

Some behind the scenes footage from the last Dodge shoot. You collect a lot of different angles and variations so they can cut together what the director has his vision on for the Final Cut. This was shot at a private club track west of Dallas where I’ve never been to before. Good times with the @porchhouse.co team and @publicissapient Agency.
It’s a good morning.
Heading out for some tropical storm surfing 😎 #hilary #tropicstorm

Fun trying different reverse 180 styles with camera moves to get the best effect while using a small parking lot in downtown LA. Great job by DP @jaredfadel with camera car driver @mossnow and the legend @robbyrubin whipping  the camera arm. Directed by @davemeyers for the @acura Slide Slide ad. #bts ##behindthescenes

We got to be Jeeple for 5 days on this amazing film shoot . Really fun getting to push the Wranglers on the sand dunes and see how amazing they performed. Sand ALL over and the eyes packed but it was all worth it . @stinastunts @huntergostunts @powers_sucks Thanks for having us Director @davemeyers and @jeep @highdiveus @radicalmedia
Thank you @acura for a fun track day . Good times with @stinastunts @rhysmillenracing and @rickytaylorrace

How was your weekend. We tried a new lake up north. Weather was not as we were hoping but we made the best of it. The TRX towed the boat like it wasn’t there and the fuel gage moved as fast too 😂 #labordayweekend #summerwentbyfast #basslake
Maserati MC20 commercial we did in Miami with David Beckham. It sure was a fun one. David and his son was great to hang with . Thank you @racingcowboys for having me again. #tbt
Play day with the M3 to capture some fun footage for a @tswalloywheels video. #tbt
Yup . That’s how I roll 😎Today !
It’s a day with lots of cameras 🎥

I’m a fan of helicopters . So this is something I really appreciate. It’s such an art to be flying them and an epic experience. Specially when you starting to get the feel of it. Great job getting us safely and with some energy around the valleys of Southern California @micahmuzio @flyingeyesworld

Lunch and lots of ideas flowing with this guy. Doctor Horse Power Nik, founder of @vfengineering . One topic was. What car and how much HP would you need to get the high speed record of a drift in a car. Current record is around 189mph in a Nissan GTR. Send us some suggestions and let’s get to the drawing board .

Here is a way back Friday. Ken Block, Tanner Foust, Stefhan Verdier, ACP and myself at the Colosseum X-Games Rally Cross. After watching the Motocross race last weekend at the historic stadium it felt appropriate to share this memory. To be honest I was in a crappy regular Rally car but with some determination and luck I made it on the podium beating the legend himself Ken Block Forever. Congrats to Foxy Foust to the 🥇 place in his Factory sponsored Ford 😘 and Brian Deegan for runner up. #waybackfriday #sparco

Doing a car swap this weekend with VF-Engineering . Gave them the M5 so let’s see if they adding some juice to it . In the mean time we will have some fun with this supercharged Huracan STO with 830hp.

The most beautiful car commercial I got to be driving for . It was done inside an ice  rink and was definitely one of the most difficult driving I’ve done due to the limited space and lack of traction . Enjoy this masterpiece Directed by Sean Thonson. #alfaromeo #waybackwednesday
20 years since my first Formula Drift Championship. Best of luck to you all tonight and go hard take chances 💪🏻 #inagrual #champion #formuladrift Picture by Mr Warren Caswell Sparco USA.

This Christmas you will get to watch Michael Mann’s long anticipated movie FERRARI. If I made the Final Cut you might see me playing Mike Hawthorn as the first British F1 Champion driving for Enzo. It truly was an experience getting to do some acting and I will always be thankful to Stunt Cordinator Robert Nagle for the opportunity. And not to forget my acting coach Patrick Dempsey who was solid encourage me and helping me out 💪🏻 #ferrarithemovie #mikehawthorn #f1 #goodtimes #hübinettestunts

Samuel Hubinette, the first FD champion, was in his first big film as a stunt driver (Fast & Furious Tokyo Drift). In one scene, he painfully learned his biggest stunt driver vs drift competitor lesson that has stuck with him ever since. You are driving for the frame, not the points. He describes the garage Tokyo Drift scene when he lost the seat to Rhys who was ready to do something that as a competitive driver he hadn’t fathomed, until then. Full interview in “Tips” at TexasDriftAcademy.com.

I’m definitely thankful everyday for my wife who is my everything. Here at the premier of a movie we can highly recommend to watch with your whole family . @jtbmovie Fantastic musical that gets you laughing and crying perhaps . Happy thanksgiving to you all 💪🏻
Throwing it back with a bunch of pictures to share many looks of the Drift cars . And still missing a few looks of the viper over the years, so more to come . #tbt

The Newport Beach Boat Parade never disappoints 😀

Just learned that one of our local Home Depot stores just alone had over $2.7 MILLION in theft 2022 . People just fill up the carts and walk out and they are not allowed to do anything. Cops don’t show up in time either . I mean what’s going on. We need a change in this country and specifically here in California. What’s your thoughts ?

Head over to Dana Point Harbor for a chance to give back to the community. The giving machine is located both at the Pacific City mall in Huntington Beach and at the Dana Point Harbor . @thegivingmachineoc #giveback
Merry Christmas and a Happy Holiday to you all from us 🌲

Ferrari the movie will be out in theaters tomorrow. Enjoy some behind the scenes footage of the making . Directed by Michael Mann and STUNT CORDINATOR Robert Nagle @rpnagle guarantees it will be a great movie . I played a small part as Mike Hawthorn,the first ever Formula One Champion from England 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿 driving for Enzo Ferrari. Made it to Colorado and Tanner put me to work right away helping him grooming his snow track 😳

So great to be back in the racing seat here at Thermal Raceway. The Lamborghini Super trofeo is a factory built race car ready to do amazing lap times. Love getting back to my old roots of racing everything from touring car racing in Sweden , Camaro cup and Viper racing league. I enjoy all disciplines of motorsport’s and the challenge to change your driving from drift to grip is such a fun challenge. Appreciate the opportunity to be part of your program VF engineering and helping develop your products .
Father of 3 and married to @stinastunts . Two time Formula Drift Champion. Rally Cross X-Games 🎖 . Movie and Commercial Stunt Driver.
